{"subject": "📊 Daily Portfolio: Markets closed | CAPR AdCom 10 days — briefing docs Jul 25", "html_body": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Daily Portfolio Check — July 19, 2026</title>\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f5f7; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #111827;\">\n\n<table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"background-color: #f4f5f7; padding: 24px 12px;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;\">\n\n        <!-- HERO BANNER -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #334155 100%); padding: 32px 24px; color: #ffffff;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #94a3b8;\">Daily Portfolio Check — Markets Closed (Weekend)</p>\n            <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 20px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #cbd5e1;\">Sunday, July 19, 2026 · Kuwait time (UTC+3) · Prices: Fri Jul 18 close</p>\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n              <tr>\n                <td>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">CAPR Unrealized P&amp;L</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: #ef4444;\">&#8722;$20.00 <span style=\"font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.8;\">(&#8722;6.14%)</span></p>\n                </td>\n                <td align=\"right\" valign=\"bottom\">\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Fri change</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #ef4444;\">&#8722;$5.44 (&#8722;1.75%)</p>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n            <p style=\"margin: 14px 0 6px 0; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #475569; font-size: 13px; color: #e2e8f0;\">&#9200; CAPR AdCom vote July 29 — <strong>10 days away</strong>. FDA briefing docs drop July 25. GTC $33–35 already set in IBKR.</p>\n            <p style=\"margin: 6px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #fbbf24;\">&#127919; Investment goal: <strong>$755.83 / $1,000</strong> — $244.17 to go <span style=\"color: #f59e0b; font-weight: 700;\">(75.6% there)</span></p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- MACRO CONTEXT -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 20px 24px 0 24px;\">\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color: #0d0d0d; border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b; border-radius: 6px;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 18px 20px;\">\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 11px; color: #f59e0b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 600;\">&#127757; Macro Context — July 19, 2026</p>\n                  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 4px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #d1d5db;\">\n                        <strong style=\"color: #fbbf24;\">Buffett Indicator:</strong>&nbsp;\n                        <span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px;\">237.9%</span>&nbsp;\n                        <span style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; background-color: #7f1d1d; color: #fca5a5; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;\">&#128308; ALL-TIME EXTREME</span>\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 4px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #d1d5db;\">\n                        <strong style=\"color: #fbbf24;\">S&amp;P 500 Forward P/E:</strong>&nbsp;\n                        <span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px;\">20.88x</span>&nbsp;\n                        <span style=\"color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;\">vs. long-term avg ~25x — AI earnings surge compressing the multiple</span>\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 4px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #d1d5db;\">\n                        <strong style=\"color: #fbbf24;\">S&amp;P 500 (Fri Jul 18):</strong>&nbsp;\n                        <span style=\"color: #ef4444; font-weight: 700;\">7,457 (&#8722;1.01%)</span>&nbsp;|&nbsp;Nasdaq <span style=\"color: #ef4444;\">&#8722;1.4%</span>&nbsp;|&nbsp;Dow <span style=\"color: #ef4444;\">&#8722;0.77%</span>\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 4px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #d1d5db;\">\n                        <strong style=\"color: #fbbf24;\">Trend:</strong>&nbsp;&#8593; Rising (Buffett) / &#8595; Falling (Forward P/E) — <em style=\"color: #9ca3af;\">split signal</em>\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </table>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 12px 0 4px 0; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #374151; font-size: 12px; color: #d1d5db; line-height: 1.65;\">Market cap is 2.4&#215; the entire US economy — a record. But forward P/E is <em>below</em> its historical average, which looks contradictory. The explanation: AI-driven earnings growth is expanding the denominator so fast that multiples appear compressed even as total valuation soars. The risk: if AI earnings growth stalls, forward P/E snaps back sharply upward, re-pricing everything.</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 6px 0 4px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; line-height: 1.65;\"><strong style=\"color: #e5e7eb;\">Implication for you:</strong> Maintain stop-losses strictly. At Buffett 238%, macro shocks produce fast, steep drawdowns. Catalyst-specific plays like CAPR are relatively insulated from macro; the risk is risk-off sentiment hitting small-cap biotech during the AdCom window (July 29 = CAPR AdCom + META earnings same day).</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 6px 0 0 0; font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; font-style: italic;\">Historical episodes at this level: 2000 dot-com peak (~190%), 2021 COVID bubble peak (~210%) — current 238% is unprecedented.</p>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- POSITION NEWS -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 20px 24px 0 24px;\">\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 18px 20px;\">\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 14px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b;\">&#128240; Position News — July 19, 2026</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-weight: 600;\">&#128309; CAPR — Capricor Therapeutics</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.65;\">\n                    <strong>Analyst action:</strong> Roth Capital (Boobalan Pachaiyappan) lowered PT to <strong>$38</strong> from $43 — maintains <span style=\"color: #059669; font-weight: 700;\">BUY</span>. Reason: NS Pharma litigation removed expected $80M milestone payment from commercial model; later modeled US launch timeline for deramiocel. Additional risk: potential $50M repayment exposure if contract rescission is ordered. <em>This is a commercial model revision, not an FDA thesis revision.</em>\n                  </p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.65;\">\n                    <strong>Consensus:</strong> 6 analysts → Strong Buy | Avg PT <strong>$49.67</strong> (+160% from $19.10 current)\n                  </p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.65;\">\n                    <strong>AdCom update:</strong> CTGTAC confirmed July 29 — reviewing BLA for deramiocel in DMD cardiomyopathy. HOPE-3 Phase 3 met ALL endpoints: primary PUL v2.0 (p=0.03), key secondary LVEF (p=0.04), all Type I error-controlled secondaries. BLA on track; PDUFA Aug 22.\n                  </p>\n                  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color: #fef9c3; border-radius: 4px;\">\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 12px; color: #854d0e; line-height: 1.6;\">\n                        &#9888;&#65039; <strong>FDA briefing documents NOT yet released</strong> — expected July 25 (6 days). This is the single most important read before the vote. FDA's internal view of the 2.4% LVEF improvement and PUL data will be visible for the first time. Run the July 25 morning check immediately. Per the plan: if FDA appears supportive → HOLD through AdCom. If FDA is clearly skeptical → consider cutting before July 29.\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </table>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- POSITIONS TABLE -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 20px 24px 0 24px;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">Position Snapshot — Fri Jul 18 close</p>\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px;\">\n              <thead>\n                <tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\">\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Status</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Ticker</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Close</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Day</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">P&amp;L $</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">P&amp;L %</th>\n                </tr>\n              </thead>\n              <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">\n                    <span style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; background-color: #fef3c7; color: #d97706; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;\">&#9888;&#65039; WATCH</span>\n                  </td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;\">CAPR <span style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400; color: #6b7280;\">16 shs</span></td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">$19.10</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;1.75%</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;$20.00</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;6.14%</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\">\n                  <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding: 12px 8px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;\">TOTAL (positions only)</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; text-align: right; color: #6b7280;\">—</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;1.75%</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;$20.00</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;6.14%</td>\n                </tr>\n              </tbody>\n            </table>\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 12px;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 14px 16px;\">\n                  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n                    <tr>\n                      <td><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;\">CAPR</span><span style=\"margin-left: 8px; padding: 2px 8px; background-color: #fef3c7; color: #d97706; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;\">&#9888;&#65039; WATCH</span></td>\n                      <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">$19.10 <span style=\"color: #dc2626; font-size: 13px;\">(&#8722;1.75%)</span></td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </table>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6;\">Down 6.14% from $20.35 entry — in the 3–7% drawdown WATCH zone. No thesis-breaking news. The Roth PT cut ($43→$38) reflects NS Pharma commercial dispute, not the FDA review. HOPE-3 data is intact. AdCom is on. Stop at $13 is 47% below current price — not in danger. This is pre-catalyst drift in a thin-float biotech. Hold.</p>\n                  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280;\"><tr><td>Stop: <strong style=\"color: #dc2626;\">$13.00</strong> (&#8722;31.9% from here)</td><td style=\"text-align: center;\">Entry: <strong style=\"color: #111827;\">$20.35</strong></td><td style=\"text-align: right;\">TP1: <strong style=\"color: #059669;\">$35.00</strong> (+83.2% from here)</td></tr></table>\n                  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; background-color: #fef3c7; border-radius: 4px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 12px; color: #92400e; font-weight: 600;\">&#128197; AdCom: July 29 (10 days) | &#128221; Briefing Docs: July 25 (6 days) | &#127919; PDUFA: Aug 22 | GTC $33–35: SET &#10003;</td></tr></table>\n                  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top: 8px; font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280;\">\n                    <tr><td style=\"padding: 3px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: #059669;\">Bull (pass, sell $34):</strong> 16 &#215; ($34&#8722;$20.35) = +$218.40 gross &#8722; $1 exit = <strong style=\"color: #059669;\">+$217.40 net</strong></td></tr>\n                    <tr><td style=\"padding: 3px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: #dc2626;\">Bear (stop at $13):</strong> 16 &#215; ($20.35&#8722;$13) = &#8722;$117.60 gross &#8722; $1 exit = <strong style=\"color: #dc2626;\">&#8722;$118.60 net</strong></td></tr>\n                    <tr><td style=\"padding: 3px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: #6b7280;\">EV at 60%:</strong> 0.60 &#215; $217.40 + 0.40 &#215; (&#8722;$118.60) = <strong style=\"color: #059669;\">+$83.20 positive</strong></td></tr>\n                  </table>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- WATCH ALERT -->\n        <tr><td style=\"padding: 12px 24px 0 24px;\">\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color: #fef9c3; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 8px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding: 14px 18px;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 4px 0; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: #92400e; text-transform: uppercase;\">&#9888;&#65039; Watch Alert — CAPR</p>\n            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #78350f; line-height: 1.6;\">CAPR &#8722;6.14% from entry. In the 3–7% drawdown Watch zone. No thesis-breaking news found. Stop at $13 not in immediate danger (47% buffer). Action: Hold. Do not pre-empt the stop.</p>\n            <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #b45309; line-height: 1.65;\"><strong>Pre-AdCom decision tree (make on July 28):</strong><br>1. <strong>HOLD through:</strong> FDA briefing docs (Jul 25) supportive of LVEF/PUL data &#8594; GTC $33–35 already set<br>2. <strong>TRIM 30–50%:</strong> Briefing docs mixed &#8594; lock partial P&amp;L, keep upside exposure<br>3. <strong>EXIT fully before Jul 29:</strong> FDA clearly skeptical &#8594; CRL risk materially higher &#8594; cut loss, redeploy</p>\n          </td></tr></table>\n        </td></tr>\n\n        <!-- FRIDAY MOVERS -->\n        <tr><td style=\"padding: 20px 24px 0 24px;\">\n          <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">&#128200;&#128201; Friday's Movers — Jul 18, 2026</p>\n          <p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; font-style: italic;\">S&amp;P &#8722;1.01% · Nasdaq &#8722;1.4% · Dow &#8722;0.77% · SMH &#8722;~9% on the week. Broad risk-off. No small-cap name clearing &#8805;20% confirmed for Jul 18.</p>\n          <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #059669;\">&#128200; Top Gainers — Jul 18</p>\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n            <thead><tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\"><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 7px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Ticker</th><th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 7px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">%</th><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 7px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Catalyst</th><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 7px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Still in play?</th></tr></thead>\n            <tbody>\n              <tr><td style=\"padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; font-weight: 600;\">TRV</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; text-align: right; color: #059669; font-weight: 600; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">+8%</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">Earnings beat — Travelers Companies insurance</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">&#10060; Insurance not halal.</td></tr>\n              <tr><td style=\"padding: 8px; font-weight: 600;\">XOM/COP/VLO</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; text-align: right; color: #059669; font-weight: 600;\">+2%</td><td style=\"padding: 8px;\">Energy — Hormuz geopolitical premium</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; color: #6b7280;\">&#10060; Macro-driven, not actionable</td></tr>\n            </tbody>\n          </table>\n          <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #dc2626;\">&#128201; Top Losers — Jul 18</p>\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n            <thead><tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\"><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 7px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Ticker</th><th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 7px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">%</th><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 7px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Catalyst</th><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 7px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Contagion to CAPR?</th></tr></thead>\n            <tbody>\n              <tr><td style=\"padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; font-weight: 600;\">NFLX</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">&#8722;10%</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">Revenue $12.56B missed consensus by $30M. EPS beat but no beat-and-raise.</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">None — zero overlap with biotech</td></tr>\n              <tr><td style=\"padding: 8px; font-weight: 600;\">SMH</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600;\">&#8722;9% (wk)</td><td style=\"padding: 8px;\">3rd weekly decline in 4 wks — semi cycle concerns</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; color: #6b7280;\">None — CAPR is biotech, uncorrelated</td></tr>\n            </tbody>\n          </table>\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 4px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 12px; color: #0c4a6e; line-height: 1.6;\">&#128269; <strong>Pattern from NFLX:</strong> Revenue missed by 0.2% yet stock fell 10%. Classic whisper-number dynamic. <strong>Signal for META July 29:</strong> consensus $60.18B revenue. Bar is $61B+ for a real pop. Factor this into same-day execution on the CAPR+META overlapping July 29.</td></tr></table>\n        </td></tr>\n\n        <!-- LARGE-CAP ON DECK -->\n        <tr><td style=\"padding: 20px 24px 0 24px;\">\n          <p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">&#127970; Large-cap on deck — next 21 days</p>\n          <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px;\">\n            <thead><tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\"><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Ticker</th><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Event</th><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Date</th><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Setup</th><th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Move</th><th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Dir.</th></tr></thead>\n            <tbody>\n              <tr><td style=\"padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; font-weight: 700;\">META</td><td style=\"padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f